data.name: Biosil Technologies Inc.
data.description:
Biosil Technologies is a global supplier of specialty ingredients for skin care, hair care and 
color cosmetics. Biosil Technologies markets a full range of silicone specialties, natural origin actives, peptides, silanols and more.

data.name: Biosil® Phytic Acid Extreme
data.description: Phytic Acid Extreme is a naturally derived ingredient sourced from rice. This material can be found in many plant sources, including corn, wheat, rice, soybean, sesame, and oat. It has a unique structure which provides self-neutralizing activity that yields gentle keratolytic effects and aids in cell turnover.

data.name: Biolsil™ Phytic Acid Extreme
data.description: Phytic Acid is a naturally sourced acid found in many plant sources, including corn, wheat, rice, soybean, sesame, and oat. Phytic Acid Extreme is a water clear 50% active solution sourced from rice.

data.name: BioPlex Cetylsil® S-PF
data.description: BioPlex® Cetylsil® S-PF is the paraben free version of our unique ingredient, BioPlex® Cetylsil® S, which combines the quaternary conditioning properties of Cetrimonium Chloride with a carboxylated silicone. BioPlex® Cetylsil® S-PF is supplied as a water soluble aqueous solution which allows a formulator to incorporate this ingredient into various systems with ease. It is ideal for use in hair care, skin care, and color cosmetics.

data.name: CAPILLISIL HAUTE CONCENTRATION®
data.description: Glycolic solution of dimethylsilanediol salicylate (high concentration silanol), obtained by the controlled hydrolysis of dimethylsilylsalicylate.

data.name: Biosil® Oligo Copper
data.description: Oligo Copper is achieved by manufacturing acetylmethionates of copper. It is water soluble, therefore ionizable. Oligo Copper is ideal for use in a wide range of cosmetic applications.

data.name: Nanospheres 100® Vitamin A Palmitate
data.description: Nanospheres 100 loaded with Vitamin A Palmitate or Retinol palmitate. Nanospheres 100 are very small sized particles (diameter around 100 nm) constituted with a porous polymer having a special structure enabling high adsorption abilities. It is ideal for use in anti-aging creams or gels, hydration and tissue regeneration, cosmetic products for care and prevention.

data.name: Nanospheres 100® Ascorbic Acid
data.description: Nanospheres 100® Ascorbic Acid are very small matricial particles made from a porous polymer. This special structure gives them good adsorption properties. Nanospheres 100® Acide Ascorbique (NCK) are "bioadhesive" particles whose affinity for proteins is obtained thanks to a functionalization of the particle by alkyl thiosulfates. It is ideal for use in any cosmetic product with an anti-free radical activity, such as anti-aging and sun products.

data.name: Biosil® Cafeisilane C
data.description: It is a limpid to slightly opalescent liquid silanol caffeinate and alginate. The main radicals are caffeine and mannuronic acid. Body contour, firming and anti-cellulite.

data.name: OKINACEA®
data.description: OKINACEA® targets both the dermal-epidermal junction and dermis. Its efficacy has been demonstrated by several ex vivo and in vitro studies. This product strengthens the DEJ functionality by stimulating both laminin-5 and collagen IV, therefore improving skin cohesion and increasing exchanges between the epidermis and dermis. OKINACEA® contributes to improve the skin structure, to firm the skin and reduce the saggy skin and consequently to delay the major signs of skin aging.

data.name: Calming Cleansing Cream
data.description: This extremely gentle soap-free cleanser is designed to quickly remove dirt and make-up leaving the skin supple, fresh and radiant. BioPlex Cetylsil S-PF makes this formula mild to your skin and eyes. Biosil EFA provides your skin with essential fatty acids which the body needs but cannot synthesize.

data.name: Cream (W/SI) with Biosil Basics I-90
data.description: Biosil Basics I-90 imparts a luxurious feel to this extraordinary lotion base formulation to which various active ingredients can be added for enhanced moisturizing, anti-aging, slimming or other concepts which can compliment your product line.

data.name: Protective Eye Serum
data.description: Algisium C creates a light serum to tighten and firm the skin around the eyes. This multi-functional ingredient also provides benefits to improve your skin such as moisturizing, anti-wrinkle, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Sea Heather helps the skin fight environmental damage caused by Reactive Oxygen Species (ROS).

data.name: W/O EMULSION BASE WITH BIOSIL BASICS I-90
data.description: Biosil Basics I-90 imparts a luxurious feel to this W/O emulsion. This lotion is an extraordinary base formulation to which various active ingredients can be added for enhanced moisturizing, anti-aging, slimming or other concepts which can compliment your product line.

data.name: Youthful Skin Serum
data.description: This crystal clear gel-serum has an elegant, nice skin feel achieved by Biowax Liquid 754. Efficiensea is an Algal sourced active ingredient which benefits your skin with a DNA protection, skin soothing and brightening effect. This serum is formulated to dramatically improve the texture of the skin overnight.

data.name: Red Rose Body Wash
data.description: Formulated for ultra-sensitive skin, this gentle body wash leaves the skin clean and soft to the touch. Biosil Basics Amphoterisil provides properties of an amphoteric surfactant and super conditioning attributes from the silicone portion of the complex.

data.name: Ageless Hand Cream
data.description: Lightoceane is a brown alga which has anti-aging properties. The appearance of ones hands reveals the sure signs of ageing. This marine solution against skin pigmentation targets and prevents age spots. In a rich hand cream, Lightoceane allows rough, dry skin to have a youthful appearance and permits mature hands to appear ageless.

data.name: Mild Body Cleanser - Self Foaming
data.description: This very gentle cleansing formula is designed to provide mild cleansing with rich lathering characteristics. BioPlex Cetysil S-PF provides skin conditioning and has a low irritation profile adding to the mildness of this formulation.

data.name: Intensive Recovery Serum
data.description: Epidermosil is a silanol with Hyaluronic Acid which stimulates cell renewal. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits; namely moisturization, wrinkle reduction, collagen production and anti-glycation. Skin regeneration and protection are intense advantages for skin‚Äôs recovery. Biowax Liquid 754 is a water soluble silicone which enhances the feel of this serum while maintaining its crystal clear character.

data.name: Super Gentle Shower Gel
data.description: This super gentle shower gel leaves the skin clean and soft to the touch. BioPlex¬¨√Ü Cetylsil¬¨√Ü S-PF significantly reduces any irritation of the surfactant system and provides softness, moisture, and cushion making it suitable for ultra-sensitive skin.

data.name: Age Renewal Night Cream
data.description: This nourishing night cream is formulated to target dry, mature skin. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits to improve skin such as moisturizing, anti-wrinkle, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Alistin provides a very strong free radical scavenging effect. Carrot Oleo Resin relieves dry skin, and Biosil EFA provides the skin with essential fatty acids. Use at night and wake up with your skin refreshed and looking younger.

data.name: Ambrosia Body Mist
data.description: Formulation #PS1-73 yields an Ambrosia Body Mist, featuring several Biosil® products.

data.name: Conditioning Clear Shampoo
data.description: This conditioning shampoo formulation can be developed clear by incorporating BioPlex Cetysil Olive CE and Biosil Basics SPQ CE in place of traditional conditioning agents. These ingredients provide manageability, good combability and shine to the hair.

data.name: Intensive Eye Repair Serum
data.description: Phyco‚ÄôDerm takes care of the delicate area around the eyes by increasing resistance against environmental stressors, smoothing fine lines and wrinkles of crow‚Äôs feet, minimizing the appearance of under-eye dark circles, and reducing the volume of under-eye bags. CAFEISILANE C2 provides the eyes additional contouring. Biowax Liquid 754 creates a luxurious feel around your eyes with this water based formulation.

data.name: Intensive Eye Repair Mask
data.description: This formulation was designed to be suitable for the Bio-Cellulose Eye Sheet from SK Bioland Co., Ltd, which we use as a delivery system for the Intensive Eye Repair Serum below. Phyco‚ÄôDerm takes care of the delicate area around the eyes by increasing resistance against environmental stressors, smoothing fine lines and wrinkles of crow‚Äôs feet, minimizing the appearance of under-eye dark circles, and reducing the volume of under-eye bags. CAFEISILANE C2 provides the eyes additional contouring. Biowax Liquid 754 creates a luxurious feel around your eyes with this water based formulation.

data.name: No Age Spot Hand Cream
data.description:
A womans hands are her calling card‚Äö Coco Chanel.
This nourishing hand cream hydrates and calms the skin. Sirhamnose improves skin tone uniformity. Biosil EFA provides the skin with essential fatty acids creating ageless effects for the skin.

data.name: Anti-Pollution Day Cream
data.description: Biosil Basics I-90 imparts a luxurious feel to this W/O emulsion. Kimarine protects the skin from daily stress to include sub exposure, cigarette smoke and exhaust fumes. Accorbosilane SP provides anti-radical activity, firming, and skin tone radiance. Biosil EFA provides the skin with essential fatty acids creating ageless effects for the skin.

data.name: Eye Contour Cream
data.description: This light and elegant cream provides the delicate skin around your eyes with multiple benefits. Meiyanol reduces dark circles and eye bags. Alistin P5 provides strong anti-aging and anti-oxidant properties. Biosil EFA provides the skin with essential fatty acids creating ageless effects for the skin. Okinacea effects collagen synthesis and restores skin volume. A very unique delivery system allows all active ingredients to penetrate effectively yet gradually into the skin.

data.name: Ageless Face Cream
data.description: Lightoceane, a unique alga, prevents the appearance of age spots and targets dry, mature skin in this nourishing face cream. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits to improve skin such as moisturizing, wrinkle reduction, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Alistin provides a very strong free radical scavenging effect. Carrot Oleo Resin relieves dry skin, and Biosil EFA provides the skin with essential fatty acids creating ageless effects for the face.

data.name: All You Need Day Cream
data.description: This light cream is a long lasting moisturizing day cream. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits to improve skin such as moisturizing, anti-wrinkle, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Alistin provides protection from the environment.

data.name: All Your Eyes Need Day and Night Cream
data.description: This light cream provides the delicate skin around your eyes with everything needed for day and night repair. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits: moisturizing, anti-wrinkle, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Alistin provides strong anti-oxidant properties and Epidermosil provides Hyaluronic Acid moisturizing properties. A very unique delivery system allows all active ingredients to penetrate effectively yet gradually into the skin.

data.name: Cellular Regenerating Firming Cream
data.description: This rich cream has a very unique structure based on a w/o emulsion achieved with Biosil Basics I-90. MS HC provides cellular regenerating and an  immediate tensing effect. Hydroxyprolisilane CN provides firming, anti-aging and anti-cellulite properties.

data.name: Cellular Repair Lotion
data.description: This rich lotion with very unique luxury structure is based on W/O emulsion achieved by Biosil Basics I-90. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits to improve skin such as moisturizing, anti-wrinkle, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Alistin provides a very strong free radical scavenging effect.

data.name: Deep Marine Moisturizing Lotion
data.description: Biosil Basics I-90 builds this water in oil formula into a rich luxurious lotion which targets moisturization and protection of the epidermal barrier. Algomega NP provides a synergistic combination of two algae rich in omega-3 fatty acids with silybum marianum seed oil which is rich in omega-6 fatty acids.  This marine derived active is great for sensitive skin and can be used for full body hydration.

data.name: Delicate Skin Relief
data.description: Ocea Defence is an active prepared from the brown macroalga, Laminaria Ochroleuca,which improves the comfort of fragile and vulnerable skin in this nourishing face cream. Lightoceane G40-EL, a unique alga, prevents the appearance of age spots and targets dry, mature skin. Biosil EFA provides the skin with essential fatty acids which the body needs but cannot synthesize.

data.name: Eye Make-up Remover
data.description: This extremely gentle cleanser is designed to remove make-up. Biosil Basics Amphoterisil and BioPlex Cetylsyl S-PF make this formula mild to the skin and non-irritant to the eyes. A combination of Aloe and Chamomile extract provides the skin with soothing and healing benefits.

data.name: Face and Body Sun Protective Lotion
data.description: This Est.SPF25 Sunscreen formulation is based on an oil and water emulsion. Biosil Basics I-90 is the key emulsifier for this luxurious system to provide excellent spreadability and skin feel resulting in uniform SPF protection. Additional UVA protection is achieved by incorporating Helinori, a natural marine derived ingredient into the formulation.  This ingredient is a genuine UVA bio-protector based on the efficacy of special marine compounds.

data.name: Firming Facial Serum #PS2-29
data.description: This very light serum is designed to repair and restore mature skin. Okinacea is a Sea Grape extract which increases GAGS. It also effects collagen synthesis and restores skin volume.

data.name: Just a Pleasure Hand Sanitizer
data.description: Biowax Liquid 754 (PEG-8 Dimethicone) is a water soluble silicone which is readily incorporated into this crystal clear sanitizer formulation to provide conditioning properties. Its soft gentle feel makes sanitizing just a pleasure leaving hands fresh and comfortable.

data.name: Moisture of the Sea Body Lotion
data.description: This light moisturizer hydrates and calms the skin. Sea Moist Complex is a combination of glycerin, seawater marine minerals and algae extract from the Philippines, specifically red algae. This complex is designed to hydrate and protect the skin from moisture loss.

data.name: No More Oily Skin Moisturizing Cream
data.description: This very light cream with a thin structure feels very comfortable on oily skin. Algisium C provides multi-functional benefits: moisturizing, anti-wrinkle, collagen production, and anti-glycation. Sebocea helps to regulate sebum secretion, inhibit excessive inflammation, and to scavenge free radicals.

data.name: Overnight Hydration and Repair Serum
data.description: This elegant formulation is designed as a night serum to complement the skins repair process, eliminate damage, and revitalize it by morning. PAE Complex¬¨√Ü Hydration and Repair provides multi-functional benefits: mild skin exfoliation, moisturization, and skin repair. OCEA CARE¬¨√Ü, which is a part of PAE Complex Hydration and Repair, utilizes the brown seaweed Laminaria saccharina to target skin repair.

data.name: Phytic Acid Resurfacing Toner
data.description: Phytic Acid Extreme is a naturally derived acid and a great alternative for alpha hydroxyl acids which are irritating to the skin.  Its mild keratolytic action allows the skin to be refreshed and have a youthful glow. This toner provides gentle exfoliating properties which allows the skin to have a resurfaced radiance.

data.name: Red Rose Face Wash
data.description: This very mild face cleansing formula is designed to remove make up and other cosmetic products from your skin. BioPlex Cetylsil S-PF makes this formula mild to the skin and non-irritating to the eyes.

data.name: Color Protective Conditioning Sulfate-free Shampoo
data.description: This elegant mild sulfate free shampoo contains Biosil Basics Amino DL-30 to provide color protection, excellent wet combing characteristics, anti-breakage benefits, superb conditioning and shine. The addition of Biosil Basics SPQ and BioPlex Cetylsil S enhance the conditioning and manageability properties. BioPlex Cetylsil S significantly reduces irritation and Biosil Basics HMV is an exclusive blend for hair moisturization.

data.name: Color Protective Lubricating and Anti-Breakage Conditioner
data.description: This formula is designed to provide conditioning from root to tip of the hair. Biosil Basics Amino DL-30 provides color protection, excellent wet combing characteristics, anti-breakage benefits, superb conditioning and shine. The addition of Biosil Basics SPQ enhances the conditioning and manageability properties and Biosil Basics HMV is an exclusive blend for hair moisturization.

data.name: Biolsil™ Carrot Oleo Resin
data.description: Biolsil™ Carrot Oleo Resin by Biosil Technologies Inc. is comprised of Daucus Carota Sativa (Carrot) Root Extract and Carrot, ext. Extractives and their physically modified derivatives such as tinctures, concretes, absolutes, essential oils, oleoresins, terpenes, terpene-free fractions, distillates, residues, etc., obtained from Daucus carota, Umbelliferae.. It is commonly used It is a Plant Origin product. Key benefits in use include: Antioxidant, Conditioning, Protection, Regenerating, Shine and radiance, Texturizing, Wrinkle prevention and Wrinkle reduction. Approved for use in DSL Listed (Canada), EINECS Listed (EU), NZIoC Listed (New Zealand) and IECIC Listed (China).

data.name: Biolsil™ Reactive Complex P
data.description: Biolsil™ Reactive Complex P by Biosil Technologies Inc. is comprised of Silicone Quaternium-2 Panthenol Succinate and PEG-8 Dimethicone. It is commonly used Key benefits in use include: Conditioning.

data.name: Biolsil™ Rose Hip Oil
data.description: Biolsil™ Rose Hip Oil by Biosil Technologies Inc. is comprised of Rosa Canina Fruit Extract and Rose, Rosa canina, ext. Extractives and their physically modified derivatives such as tinctures, concretes, absolutes, essential oils, oleoresins, terpenes, terpene-free fractions, distillates, residues, etc., obtained from Rosa canina, Rosaceae.. It is commonly used It is a Plant Origin product. Key benefits in use include: Anti stretch marks, Anti-aging, Moisturizing, Regenerating, Smoothing, Texturizing, Wrinkle prevention and Wrinkle reduction.

data.name: Biolsil™ EFA
data.description: Biosil EFA is an essential fatty acid (Vitamin F) complex offering an elegant and easy to use blend of materials which have long been recognized as essentials for healthy looking skin. Biosil EFA is based on Omega-6 Linoleic Acid and Omega-3 alpha-Linolenic Acid, the only long chain fatty acid the body needs but cannot synthesize.

data.name: Biolsil™ Fluorosil Cyclic Fluoro Guerbet 3.5
data.description: Biosil Basics Fluoro Guerbet 3.5 is a highly emollient ester. Guerbet esters have low irritation potentials with low volatility, excellent lubricity and stability.

data.name: Biolsil™ Rice Bran Oil
data.description: Biolsil™ Rice Bran Oil by Biosil Technologies Inc. is comprised of Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil and Fats and Glyceridic oils, rice bran. It is commonly used It is a Plant Origin product. Key benefits in use include: Antioxidant, Conditioning, Moisturizing and Smoothing. Approved for use in DSL Listed (Canada), EINECS Listed (EU), NZIoC Listed (New Zealand), TSCA Compliant and IECIC Listed (China).
